Package: cdi-mp
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: CrystalDiskInfo MP - Web-based disk health monitoring tool
 CrystalDiskInfo MP is a cross-platform web-based disk health monitoring
 tool that reads S.M.A.R.T./NVMe data directly via OS-level IOCTL/ioctl
 calls. No external tools (smartmontools, etc.) required.
 .
 Features:
  - Web-based UI with CrystalDiskInfo-style frontend
  - Anime theme support
  - 70+ language support
  - Temperature history charts
  - Real-time disk health monitoring
